content: The power of our competitive advantage comes from the compounding effects of 3 hard problems that we've solved: first, we've built a reverse logistics supply chain that has created a massive and seemingly endless supply advantage in the resale market; second, we've built world-class infrastructure, technology and software to process single SKU apparel at scale; and third, we've built a data-driven managed marketplace that connects buyers and sellers on our platform and get smarter with each item that we process, now more than 125 million items and counting.
